folder: Grand Street & Havemeyer Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
305-327 Grand Street, north side, at Havemeyer Street (center). The view shows the Unique Theatre alias "The Bum" razed in 1923 on the N.W. corner of Havemeyer street. 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
